    "Training and evaluations across carbon sources.",
    "To the evaluations in Fig. 3C, for each MFG the training and early stopping folds were chosen with a 4:1 ratio; in all cases we tested each model on all nodes of the other MFGs.",
    "Following the same scheme as in the previous section, the best performing model on the early stopping set was chosen for the evaluation of the test set; the training set was resampled 5 times and each model was retrained 10 times with different initial weights.",
